nd":"italic_en","text":"an imaginary form,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayaAlN","text_ar":"خَيَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming in sleep;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, K;) one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tayofu xayaAlK","text_ar":"طَيْفُ خَيَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifu","text_ar":"طَايِفُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayaAlK","text_ar":"خَيَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning thus]: (IDrd, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything that obscures the sight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arising"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a vain suggestion of the Devil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a jinnee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a human being,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayaAl","text_ar":"خَيَال"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"visits, a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in sleep"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1906},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifN","text_ar":"طَايِفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so says IF in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Twf","text_ar":"طوف"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) both of these words signify alike; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayaAl","text_ar":"خَيَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that comes to one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"visits one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiyfN","text_ar":"طِيفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayaAl","text_ar":"خَيَال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, TA:) or ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayofN","text_ar":"طَيْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is properly, or originally, an inf. n.; and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tayofu AlxayaAli","text_ar":"طَيْفُ الخَيَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the coming of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xyAl","text_ar":"خيال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in sleep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K: *) accord. to El-Mufaddal, (O,) one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayofN","text_ar":"طَيْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifu xayaAlK","text_ar":"طَايِفُ خَيَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it is originally ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayowifN","text_ar":"طَيْوِفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and then]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ifN","text_ar":"طَيِّفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"may~itN","text_ar":"مَيِّتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mayotN","text_ar":"مَيْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAta","text_ar":"مَاتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yamuwtu","text_ar":"يَمُوتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tayofu","text_ar":"طَيْفُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ayoTaAni","text_ar":"الشَّيْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifuhu","text_ar":"طَايِفُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Devil's visitation, by touch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"madness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"insanity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@lomas~i","text_ar":"بِا@لْمَسِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by vain prompting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suggestion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayofN mina Al$~ayoTaAni","text_ar":"طَيْفٌ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A touch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slight degree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a taint"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an infection"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of insanity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possession, from the Devil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamamN","text_ar":"لَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; occurring in the Kur vii. 200, accord. to one reading; another reading being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Al$~ayoTaAni","text_ar":"مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^ifN","text_ar":"طَايِفٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies the same. (S, O. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawofN","text_ar":"طَوْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tayofu","text_ar":"طَيْفُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnK","text_ar":"جُنُونٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A touch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slight degree, of insanity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diabolical possession"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TayofN","text_ar":"طَيْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Insanity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diabolical possession:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) so says A 'Obeyd, on the authority of ElAhmar: (TA:) and this is said by Az to be the meaning of the word in the language of the Arabs. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(I'Ab, Mujáhid, O, K:) because the intellect of the angry departs [for a time] so that he assumes the the likeness of the insane, or possessed: (O, TA:) said by I'Ab to mean thus in the Kur vii. 200. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IDrd","O","Lth","TA","Msb","Fr","Kr","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27479","headword_ar":"طِيفٌ","root":"Tyf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}